previous.excerpt: VogueAI is a complete AI-driven solution for any digital content with fashion. This solution can take any movie, web series, or short videos and detect keyframes with uniques fashion trends in entire video sequences.
previous.title: VogueAI - Automated fashion extraction from videos

localize.description: VogueAI是一个完整的AI驱动的解决方案，适用于任何与时尚有关的数字内容。该解决方案可以将任何电影、网络系列或短视频，在整个视频序列中检测具有独特时尚趋势的关键帧。
localize.tagline: 从视频中自动提取时装

localize.description: VogueAI是一個完整的AI驅動的解決方案，適用於任何與時尚有關的數字內容。該解決方案可以將任何電影、網絡系列或短視頻，在整個視頻序列中檢測具有獨特時尚趨勢的關鍵幀。
localize.tagline: 從視頻中自動提取時裝

next.excerpt: With Capsule you can collaborate and leave feedback directly on top of any website. Just one click to comment, and another to share it with the world! We automatically organize your feedback in the dashboard. Click —> Comment —> Share & repeat!
